                    <item>
              <title>Using social media to develop your own professional learning network - SEDA parallel session 4</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5978</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5978</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p><br />Twitter: <a rel="nofollow" href="http://twitter.com/#!/suebecks">@<strong>suebecks</strong></a> and <a rel="nofollow" href="http://twitter.com/#!/drdjwalker">@<strong>drdjwalker</strong></a> #sedapln / PLN<br /><br />...</p>
