                    <item>
              <title>A quick (PechaKucha 20x20) tour of Creative Commons Licensing</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3825</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3825</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>Presentation by Karen Cropper<br />Project and Liaison Manager, OLnet<br />Institute of Educational Technology, The Open University<br />Presentation prepared for the &lsquo;Learning in an Open World&rsquo; online conference 22-23 June 2010 <a href="/cloudscape/view/2012">http://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloudscape/view/2012</a></p>]]></description>
