              <description><![CDATA[<p><em>Programme director at NSF</em></p>
<p>Focus on cyberlearning and how this is being developed in NSF programmes</p>
<p><strong><em>Technology, education and policy in 40 minutes&hellip;</em></strong></p>
<ul>
