<p>Unified modelling language - uses severl differnet visualisations</p>
<p>Some possibilities (tabs to different representations)</p>
<ul>
    <li>Content view</li>
    <li>Annotation view - great out and doodle on it in free form</li>
    <li>Resizable boxes to indicate the importance of different activities</li>
    <li>Alternative shapes view</li>
    <li>Compentencies view </li>
    <li>Suggested data flow view (with imagined data, condition/branch and group flows)</li>
    <li>Individual learner view showing individual, group adn whole class task</li>
    <li>Time view</li>
